reviewText: I certainly forget this movie DVD.  Falling asleep.

This is such a great collection for the price.  As I've written before in DVD reviews on Amazon...I cannot believe how much less movies cost now than they did 10-15 years ago.  Night of the Living Dead is one of my all time favorite  movies. Zombie Strippers is silly, gory fun. This is a solid 4 pick for the price.
Night of the living dead is a cult classic. The Devils tomb while not a classic ain't bad.
